### 2. State Transition Logic

#### a. Ensure Proper State Transition
Make sure that the `EnterState` method in `PlayerMoveState` is being called. If the transition is happening every frame, it might be that the state is not being retained properly. By implementing the input handling logic as suggested above, you should only transition when the input changes.

